                        <interp inst="t18440205-name-1401" type="surname" value="FIELD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440205-name-1401" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of counterfeit coin to the Mint. This is a counterfeit shilling.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Is it a good imitation? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I should say it is rather inferior—it might impose on a person not well acquainted with money.</p>
